metadata.name: I Dreamed About Love #1
metadata.description:
Welcome to the world of Toigo’s Door!

“I Dreamed About Love” is the NFT companion single to Toigo’s new EP, “I Feel This Love Turn Cold” and serves as your key into the world of Toigo’s Door.

Music, art, gaming, community.

Welcome to Toigo’s Door

“I Dreamed About Love”

Written by Toigo 

 Produced by Brian Howes 

 Engineered by Karl Dicarie 

 Mixed by Mark Needam 

 Mastered by Chris Gehringer 

 Guitars: Ryan Stead & Toigo 

 Bass: Mike Young 

 Drums: Pat Stewart 

 Keys and Vocals: Toigo
